<plot>Palak-Behind shut eyes is a story dealing with a psychological condition called rapid eye movement behavior disorder (RBD). The main protagonist Sonali get caught in a web of dream and reality where she is not able to distinguish the line between the two and experiences the weird situation one could face while suffering from the disorder. She is a psychology student arriving in Pune to complete her project "Dreams &amp; Reality". The people around her Dr.Mathur, Saahil, Sagar, Tarana, and Santokh Singh all seem different in the 'other world', the world between dreams and reality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420856</url></doc>
